						<p>
							Alisa found her apartment on Rendin and liked the deposit-free process. Two weeks before move-in, she spent three evenings comparing movers on Google, reading Estonian-language reviews she could barely parse, and getting quotes that varied wildly. She picked by gut feel and paid too much.
						</p>
						<p class="persona-quote">"I trusted Rendin for the contract — I'd have trusted them if they'd recommended a mover too."</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="persona">
					<div class="persona-avatar" style="background: rgba(12, 124, 120, 0.1);">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
					<div class="persona-content">
						<h4>Mihkel & Kadri, 34 & 32</h4>
						<p class="persona-role">Family · Upgrading from 2BR to 3BR in Kristiine, Tallinn</p>
						<div class="persona-tags">
							<span class="ptag ptag-pain">Moving with kids</span>
							<span class="ptag ptag-pain">Large volume</span>
