				</div>

				<div class="callout">
					<p class="callout-label">Common thread</p>
					<p>None of them struggle to find <em>a</em> mover. The problem is finding a <em>trustworthy</em> one at a fair price — and trust is exactly what Rendin has already built. That equity transfers.</p>
